Privacy Policy for Pointless Button

Last updated: [Date]

Thank you for using Pointless Button! This Privacy Policy outlines our approach to user information for our app.

1. Data Collection:

Pointless Button does not collect any personal information or data from its users. Your privacy is important, and we have designed the app to operate without the need for any user data.
2. Offline Functionality:

Pointless Button operates entirely offline. There is no requirement for an internet connection to use the app, and your interactions with the button remain on your device.
3. No Ads:

Our app does not display advertisements. Pointless Button is free from distractions, allowing you to enjoy its simplicity without interruptions.
4. Permissions:

Pointless Button does not require any special device permissions. The app respects your device's privacy settings and focuses solely on its core functionality.
5. Data Security:

Since Pointless Button does not collect any data, there is no user information stored or transmitted. Your privacy and the security of your information are of utmost importance to us.
6. Updates:

This privacy policy may be updated as needed. Users will be notified of any changes through app updates or other means.
7. Contact Information:

If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at [Your Contact Email Address].
8. Compliance:

We strive to comply with all relevant privacy laws and regulations. If you believe there is a problem with how we handle your data, please contact us so we can address the issue promptly.
By using Pointless Button, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. We appreciate your simplicity and trust in our app.

Thank you for choosing Pointless Button!
